      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/4/7/11",
      "text": [
        ": سمعت أبا جعفر عليه السلام يقول: من الامور امور موقوفة عند الله يقدم منها ما يشاء ويؤخر منها ما يشاء"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "11. [11/369] al-Kafi: Muhammad b. Ismail from al-Fadhl b. Shadhan from Hammad from Rib’i from al-Fudhayl who said: I heard Aba Ja’far عليه السلام saying: From the matters are matters which are deferred with Allah. He brings forward from them what He wills and puts back from them what He wills."
        ]
      }
    },
